    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔王：和平缔造者》是一款黑暗奇幻古典RPG，你能自订种族、性别与职业，召集你中意的伙伴加入队伍，并透过选择改变角色与世界的命运。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创建人物吧</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能自订种族、性别、名字、职业与非战斗技能，创造独特的主角。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你想跟谁一起冒险？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类圣职者、暗精灵巡林客或半兽人捍卫者？组一个对你而言最强的队伍吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择会影响剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能决定要怎么跟邻国的人互动，但小心──你可能会挑起战争。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重视合作的回合制战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同职业各有优缺点，必须互补才能获胜。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要人物 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/f396a7976f32ef29c859019dc6d5d71a.avif?t=1732503360\" width=544 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魔王</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >活了五百年的魔族君主，决心终结魔族与人类常年的斗争。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/66b30e2486ab4181d6ac20ea35b6d419.avif?t=1732503360\" width=544 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>勇者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传说中勇者的子孙，心怀着驱逐魔族的使命。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/0007850ca3af4fac7baf887e7d030ae2.avif?t=1732503360\" width=544 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人类圣职者「友爱」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >边境圣所的圣职者，渇望创造众生平等的世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/422a238f743fdde2a1140a5f6abe7019.avif?t=1732503360\" width=544 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>暗精灵巡林客「猛毒」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擅长剑术与弓术的暗精灵，至友遭勇者杀害。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/6c2ff1e48c541406b56798d7c6749916.avif?t=1732503360\" width=544 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>半兽人捍卫者「郊狼」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部落出身的少年战士，渇望人类与暗精灵的接纳。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/d898765f5f70994b15bde179b4e9bc54.avif?t=1732503360\" width=544 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>尸体苏生者「血红」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >錬金术与死灵术的大师，为了目的不择手段。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1294380/extras/d927567ad7649d72dbcfb486a66b96dd.avif?t=1732503360\" width=544 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>东方战士「竹刀」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔王猫工作室《骰子魔塔：光辉王女》的主角，来自东南的银白王国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直播与游戏实况之规范</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许直播与游戏实况。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许营利，但仅限于以影音网站的功能营利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若能在直播或游戏实况的标题加入游戏名称，或在说明栏列出Steam页面的连结，我方将不胜感激。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直播与游戏实况所导致的任何损害，我方概不负责。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本规范如有变更，恕不另行通知。</p></li></ul>",
